@startuml
' Domain: invoice  |  mode: full
' Edge legend: --> ORM relationship()   ..> FK-only (no relationship)
hide empty members
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam classFontSize 13
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam ClassBorderColor #888888
skinparam ClassBackgroundColor #FAFAFA

class Invoice <<invoices>> {
  +id : int <<PK>>
  +charge_id : int <<FK→charges>>
  +provider : str
  +external_invoice_id : str
  +document_url : str?
  +issued_at : datetime
  +created_at : datetime
}

' FK-only links (no ORM relationship declared):
Invoice ..> Charge : charge_id

